providers.name: TZM-bl Neutralization (NAb)
providers.description: Imports a specially formatted TSV, CSV or Excel file. Measures neutralization in TZM-bl cells as a function of a reduction in Tat-induced luciferase (Luc) reporter gene expression after a single round of infection. Montefiori, D.C. 2004?

providers.name: TZM-bl Neutralization (NAb), High-throughput (Cross Plate Dilution)
providers.description: Imports a specially formatted CSV or XLS file that contains data from multiple plates. The high-throughput NAb assay differs from the standard NAb assay in that dilutions are assumed to occur across plates, rather than within a single plate. Both NAb assay types measure neutralization in TZM-bl cells as a function of a reduction in Tat-induced luciferase (Luc) reporter gene expression after a single round of infection. Montefiori, D.C. 2004?

providers.name: TZM-bl Neutralization (NAb), High-throughput (Single Plate Dilution)
providers.description: Imports a specially formatted CSV or XLS file that contains data from multiple plates. This high-throughput NAb assay differs from the standard NAb assay in that samples are identical across plates but with a different virus per plate. Dilutions are assumed to occur within a single plate. Both NAb assay types measure neutralization in TZM-bl cells as a function of a reduction in Tat-induced luciferase (Luc) reporter gene expression after a single round of infection. Montefiori, D.C. 2004?

providers.name: Viability
providers.description: Imports Guava ViaCount and ExpressPlus cell count and viability data.
